      <title>人民币接近红线后中国维持人民币防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-maintains-yuan-defense-after-it-tests-policy-red-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元坚挺和市场情绪不佳的压力，中国坚持支持人民币的持有模式，使其接近政策红线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-maintains-yuan-defense-after-it-tests-policy-red-line</guid>
