      <title>亚洲股市追随美国就业增长，油价下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/asian-stocks-set-for-gains-eyes-on-daily-yuan-fix-markets-wrap</link>
